# Skill Precedence

If multiple skill triggers match in the same request, read and follow the
matching skill files in this exact order:

1. `@.agents/skills/turborepo/SKILL.md`
2. `@.agents/skills/hono/SKILL.md`
3. `@.agents/skills/better-auth-best-practices/SKILL.md`
